title: Tony Romo Live! & Veteran QBs under pressure
itunes:title: Tony Romo Live! & Veteran QBs under pressure
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – speak with Cowboys quarterback Tony Romo about the upcoming season, the running back battle and his new DirecTV commercial. The guys then break down veteran signal callers who have the most to prove this season. Finally, NFL Media Insider Ian Rapoport joins the show to dive into the latest storylines around training camp.
